  99:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****    [..]
 100:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****      (+) To write to the RTC Backup Data registers, use the HAL_RTCEx_BKUPWrite()
 101:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****          function.
 102:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****      (+) To read the RTC Backup Data registers, use the HAL_RTCEx_BKUPRead()
 103:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****          function.
 104:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****      (+) Before calling these functions you have to call HAL_RTC_Init() in order to
 105:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****          perform TAMP base address offset calculation.
 106:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c **** 
