 161:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @brief  Set TimeStamp.
 162:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @note   This API must be called before enabling the TimeStamp feature.
 163:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @param  hrtc RTC handle
 164:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @param  TimeStampEdge Specifies the pin edge on which the TimeStamp is
 165:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *         activated.
 166:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
 167:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_TIMESTAMPEDGE_RISING: the Time stamp event occurs on the
 168:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *                                        rising edge of the related pin.
 169:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_TIMESTAMPEDGE_FALLING: the Time stamp event occurs on the
 170:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *                                         falling edge of the related pin.
 171:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @param  RTC_TimeStampPin specifies the RTC TimeStamp Pin.
 172:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
 173:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_TIMESTAMPPIN_DEFAULT: PC13 is selected as RTC TimeStamp Pin.
 174:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *               The RTC TimeStamp Pin is per default PC13, but for reasons of
 175:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *               compatibility, this parameter is required.
 176:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @retval HAL status
 177:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   */
