 864:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @brief  Set the Smooth calibration parameters.
 865:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @note   To deactivate the smooth calibration, the field SmoothCalibPlusPulses
 866:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *         must be equal to SMOOTHCALIB_PLUSPULSES_RESET and the field
 867:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *         SmoothCalibMinusPulsesValue must be equal to 0.
 868:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @param  hrtc RTC handle
 869:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @param  SmoothCalibPeriod  Select the Smooth Calibration Period.
 870:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *          This parameter can be can be one of the following values :
 871:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_SMOOTHCALIB_PERIOD_32SEC: The smooth calibration period is 32s.
 872:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_SMOOTHCALIB_PERIOD_16SEC: The smooth calibration period is 16s.
 873:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_SMOOTHCALIB_PERIOD_8SEC: The smooth calibration period is 8s.
 874:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @param  SmoothCalibPlusPulses  Select to Set or reset the CALP bit.
 875:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
 876:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_SMOOTHCALIB_PLUSPULSES_SET: Add one RTCCLK pulse every 2*11 pulses.
 877:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_SMOOTHCALIB_PLUSPULSES_RESET: No RTCCLK pulses are added.
 878:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @param  SmoothCalibMinusPulsesValue  Select the value of CALM[8:0] bits.
 879:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *          This parameter can be one any value from 0 to 0x000001FF.
 880:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @retval HAL status
 881:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   */
